---
---

<section id="pricing" class="section section-tinted" aria-labelledby="pricing-heading">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Packages</div>
      <h2 id="pricing-heading" class="section-h2">
        Simple website and care packages<br>
        <span class="text-amber">for small businesses, nationwide.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subline">Start with a one-time website build, then keep the technical side managed with a monthly care plan. Professional business email can be added when your business needs it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-phase-row reveal" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="pricing-phase pricing-phase-once">
        <span class="pricing-phase-num">01</span>
        <span class="pricing-phase-lbl">One-time website build</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-phase-arrow">→ then choose</div>
      <div class="pricing-phase pricing-phase-monthly">
        <span class="pricing-phase-num">02</span>
        <span class="pricing-phase-lbl">Monthly care plan</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-grid">

      <div class="pricing-card reveal" data-tier="website-build">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <div class="tier-label">Website Build</div>
          <h3 class="tier-name">Landing Page Website</h3>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="price-sign">$</span>
            <span class="price-num">1,000</span>
            <span class="price-per">upfront</span>
          </div>
          <p class="tier-line">For local businesses that need a clean, professional one-page website to explain their services and generate enquiries.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="tier-feats" role="list">
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Custom landing page website</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Mobile-friendly design</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Contact form setup</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Phone, email and WhatsApp enquiry buttons</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Basic SEO setup</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Secure HTTPS setup</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Hosting setup and domain connection</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Google Search Console setup</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Launch support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">Start Website Build</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card pricing-featured reveal reveal-delay-1" data-tier="managed-care">
        <div class="featured-crown">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="tier-top">
          <div class="tier-label tier-label-amber">Monthly Care</div>
          <h3 class="tier-name">Managed Website Care</h3>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="price-sign">$</span>
            <span class="price-num">100</span>
            <span class="price-per">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="tier-line">For businesses that want the website, hosting, domain, forms, SSL and basic SEO checks managed every month.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="tier-feats" role="list">
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Website hosting management</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Domain and DNS checks</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> SSL monitoring</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Contact form testing</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> WhatsApp, phone and email link checks</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Basic SEO monitoring</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Google Search Console checks</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Small monthly updates</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Standard domain renewal allowance</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Basic security checks</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-amber btn-full">View Monthly Care</a>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card reveal reveal-delay-2" data-tier="care-plus">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <div class="tier-label">Care Plus</div>
          <h3 class="tier-name">Website Care Plus</h3>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="price-sign">$</span>
            <span class="price-num">150</span>
            <span class="price-per">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="tier-line">For businesses that want extra monthly support, blog uploads or help managing website content updates.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="tier-feats" role="list">
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Everything in Managed Website Care</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Extra monthly support</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> One client-supplied blog upload per month</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Blog formatting</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> SEO title and meta setup for blog posts</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Priority support</li>
          <li><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 7.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-6.5" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Option to add professional business email</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">Ask About Care Plus</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="addons-divider" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="addons-divider-line"></div>
      <span class="addons-divider-label">Add-ons &amp; Extras</span>
      <div class="addons-divider-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="offer-grid offer-grid-addons reveal reveal-delay-2" aria-label="ReadyStack Digital add-ons">
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Add-on</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Professional business email</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Add email such as info@yourdomain.com, with support for MX, SPF, DKIM and DMARC records.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Add-on</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Monthly social media content</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Optional monthly content support for social posts, blog posts and branded content updates across Instagram, Facebook, TikTok and LinkedIn — <a href="/social">see social media support</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Add-on</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Extra blog uploads</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Client-supplied blog posts can be uploaded, formatted and prepared with basic SEO settings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offer-card">
        <div class="offer-kicker">Quoted separately</div>
        <h3 class="svc-name">Extra pages or custom requests</h3>
        <p class="svc-desc">Additional pages, advanced SEO, content writing, logos and custom features are quoted based on scope.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-page-cta reveal">
      <a href="/packages" class="btn btn-amber btn-lg">Compare all packages</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Get a tailored quote</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing-page-cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  /* Add-ons grid: balance four cards across the row */
  .offer-grid-addons {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }
  .offer-grid-addons .svc-desc a {
    color: var(--amber-600);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
  }
  .offer-grid-addons .svc-desc a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .offer-grid-addons { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .offer-grid-addons { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
